Interface LocalMediaProvider.ILocalMediaProviderCallback

LocalMediaProvider
public static interface LocalMediaProvider.ILocalMediaProviderCallback

This interface defines a callback function to be called when the root container is ready after a call to LocalMediaProvider.getLocalMediaProvider(Activity, com.tversity.airflinger.sdk.android.assets.MediaObject.MediaObjectType, boolean, com.tversity.airflinger.sdk.android.assets.LocalMediaProvider.ILocalMediaProviderCallback) The callback is asynchronous, and returned on the UI thread.
